description.en: Rocky Inu ! Inspired by the hottest memecoin to hit the market in recent times unlike Bitcoin Rocky Inu is a Deflationary Token which means the total supply is always decreasing, making it more and more rare. That charges Tax fees on everything but Buys. The fees charged on all Non-Buy Transactions out of which percentage of the coins are burned, but holding does reward you in the end.
